# CurveLens Copper cron template — intentionally non-executable.
#
# Copper is experimental. Do not register or enable schedules from this file.
# A reviewed future schedule must create an isolated agent turn with
# CCVM_PRODUCT=copper, read AGENTS.md plus deployments/copper/AGENTS.md,
# acquire and verify the exact Section 64 bulletin, and invoke
# `$curvelens-daily-analysis`. It must resume persisted state, default to no
# delivery, and ship disabled for explicit approval.
